dc_title_s: Revised plan of Ocean Gate, Ocean County, New Jersey, section no. 2
dc_description_s: This revised plan of Ocean Gate consists of 6 pieces to be assembled 112-298. It is a negative photostat in worn out condition. Available technology enabled a complete assemblage of the six component maps and the image is available here.|Source map supplied by New Jersey Department of Environmental Protection|Handwritten inscription in bottom right corner says: "Please return this map to L. F. Wagner, 18 Allen St., Toms River, N.J."
